823uint8_t sse::add_epu8(__m128i a) noexcept {
824 auto b = shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 2, 3, 2)>(a);
825 a = add(a, b, uint8_t());
826 b = zeros();
827 a = sad_epu8(a, b);
828 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint8_t>(a);
829}
830
831uint16_t sse::add_epu16(__m128i a) noexcept {
832 a = add(a, shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 2, 3, 2)>(a), uint16_t());
833 a = add(a, shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(1, 1, 1, 1)>(a), uint16_t());
834 a = add(a, srli<2>(a), uint16_t());
835 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint16_t>(a);
836}
837
838uint32_t sse::add_epu32(__m128i a) noexcept {
839 a = add(a, shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 2, 3, 2)>(a), uint32_t());
840 a = add(a, shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(1, 1, 1, 1)>(a), uint32_t());
841 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint32_t>(a);
842}
843
844uint64_t sse::add_epu64(__m128i a) noexcept {
845 a = add(a, shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 2, 3, 2)>(a), uint64_t());
846 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint64_t>(a);
847}

869template <int imm8>
870__m128i sse::alignr(__m128i a, __m128i b) noexcept {
871 static_assert(imm8 >= 0 && imm8 <= 16, "imm8 must be in range [0, 16]");
872 constexpr int s = imm8 & 0x1F;
873 #if WJR_HAS_SIMD(SSSE3)
874 return _mm_alignr_epi8(a, b, s);
875 #else
876 if constexpr (s == 0) {
877 return b;
878 }
879 if constexpr (s == 16) {
880 return a;
881 }
882 if constexpr (s < 16) {
883 if constexpr (s == 8) {
884 return shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(2, 1, 0, 3)>(a, b);
885 } else {
886 return Or(slli<16 - s>(a), srli<s>(b));
887 }
888 }
889 WJR_UNREACHABLE();
890 #endif // SSSE3
891}

895}

1185template <int imm8>
1186int sse::extract_epi8(__m128i a) noexcept {
1187 static_assert(imm8 >= 0 && imm8 < 16, "imm8 must be in range [0, 15]");
1188 #if WJR_HAS_SIMD(SSE4_1)
1189 return _mm_extract_epi8(a, imm8);
1190 #else
1191 if constexpr (imm8 & 1) {
1192 return extract_epi16<(imm8 >> 1)>(a) >> 8;
1193 } else {
1194 return extract_epi16<(imm8 >> 1)>(a) & 0xff;
1195 }
1196 #endif
1197}
1198
1199template <int imm8>
1200int sse::extract_epi16(__m128i a) noexcept {
1201 static_assert(imm8 >= 0 && imm8 < 8, "imm8 must be in range [0, 7]");
1202 return _mm_extract_epi16(a, imm8);
1203}
1204
1205template <int imm8>
1206int sse::extract_epi32(__m128i a) noexcept {
1207 static_assert(imm8 >= 0 && imm8 < 4, "imm8 must be in range [0, 3]");
1208 #if WJR_HAS_SIMD(SSE4_1)
1209 return _mm_extract_epi32(a, imm8);
1210 #else
1211 if constexpr (imm8 == 0) {
1212 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint32_t>(a);
1213 } else if constexpr (imm8 == 1) {
1214 return static_cast<uint32_t>(simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint64_t>(a) >> 32);
1215 } else if constexpr (imm8 == 2) {
1216 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint32_t>(shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 2, 3, 2)>(a));
1217 } else {
1218 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint32_t>(shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 3, 3, 3)>(a));
1219 }
1220 #endif
1221}
1222
1223template <int imm8>
1224int64_t sse::extract_epi64(__m128i a) noexcept {
1225 static_assert(imm8 >= 0 && imm8 < 2, "imm8 must be in range [0, 1]");
1226 #if WJR_HAS_SIMD(SSE4_1)
1227 return _mm_extract_epi64(a, imm8);
1228 #else
1229 if constexpr (imm8 == 0) {
1230 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint64_t>(a);
1231 } else {
1232 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint64_t>(shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 2, 3, 2)>(a));
1233 }
1234 #endif
1235}

1502uint8_t sse::min_epu8(__m128i a) noexcept {

1504 a = min_epu8(a, srli_epi16(a, 8));
1505 a = _mm_minpos_epu16(a);
1506 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint8_t>(a);
1507 #else
1508 a = min_epu8(a, shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 2, 3, 2)>(a));
1509 a = min_epu8(a, shufflelo_epi16<_MM_SHUFFLE(1, 0, 3, 2)>(a));
1510 a = min_epu8(a, shufflelo_epi16<_MM_SHUFFLE(1, 0, 1, 0)>(a));
1511 auto X = simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint32_t>(a);
1512 return std::min((uint8_t)X, (uint8_t)(X >> 8));
1513 #endif
1514}
1515
1516uint16_t sse::min_epu16(__m128i a) noexcept {
1517 #if WJR_HAS_SIMD(SSE4_1)
1518 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint16_t>(_mm_minpos_epu16(a));
1519 #else
1520 a = min_epu16(a, shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 2, 3, 2)>(a));
1521 a = min_epu16(a, shufflelo_epi16<_MM_SHUFFLE(1, 0, 3, 2)>(a));
1522 a = min_epu16(a, shufflelo_epi16<_MM_SHUFFLE(1, 0, 1, 0)>(a));
1523 return simd_cast<__m128i_t, uint16_t>(a);
1524 #endif
1525}

1527uint32_t sse::min_epu32(__m128i a) noexcept {
1528 a = min_epu32(a, shuffle_epi32<_MM_SHUFFLE(3, 2, 3, 2)>(a));
1529 a = min_epu32(a, shufflelo_epi16<_MM_SHUFFLE(1, 0, 3, 2)>(a));

1531}

1727template <int imm>
1728__m128i sse::shl(__m128i a) noexcept {
1729 if constexpr (imm >= 64) {
1730 a = slli<8>(a);
1731 a = slli_epi64(a, imm - 64);
1732 return a;
1733 } else {
1734 auto b = slli_epi64(a, imm);
1735 auto c = slli<8>(a);
1736 c = srli_epi64(c, 64 - imm);
1737 return Or(b, c);
1738 }
1739}

1743 if constexpr (imm >= 64) {
1744 a = srli<8>(a);
1745 a = srli_epi64(a, imm - 64);
1746 return a;
1747 } else {
1748 auto b = srli_epi64(a, imm);
1749 auto c = srli<8>(a);
1750 c = slli_epi64(c, 64 - imm);
1751 return Or(b, c);
1752 }
1753}
